---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = 'July 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — PromoStrats"
  description="How PromoStrats collects, uses and protects the personal information you share when you get in touch or work with me."
>
  <div class="ps2-legal">
    <div class="ps2-wrap">
      <span class="ps2-eyebrow">// legal</span>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="ps2-legal-updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="ps2-legal-body">
        <p>
          This policy explains what personal information PromoStrats ("I", "me") collects, why, and what your rights are.
          PromoStrats is a freelance Shopify design and SEO service based in London, run by Connor Bawcutt.
        </p>

        <h2>Who I am</h2>
        <p>
          PromoStrats, London, United Kingdom. You can reach me at
          <a href="mailto:promostrats@gmail.com">promostrats@gmail.com</a>. For the purposes of UK GDPR, I am the data
          controller for the information described here.
        </p>

        <h2>What I collect</h2>
        <p>
          When you submit the contact form, I collect the details you choose to give me — typically your name, email
          address, phone number, your website URL, and the message you send. I do not collect special-category personal
          data, and I don't ask for it.
        </p>

        <h2>Why I collect it</h2>
        <p>
          I use this information solely to respond to your enquiry, arrange a strategy call, and, if we work together, to
          deliver and manage that work. My lawful basis is your consent when you contact me, and legitimate interest in
          responding to and administering the services you've asked about.
        </p>

        <h2>How it's handled</h2>
        <p>
          Contact form submissions are processed and delivered to my email inbox through Formspree, a third-party form
          provider. Your message is stored in my email account so I can reply and keep a record of our conversation. I
          don't sell your data, and I don't share it with anyone except where necessary to provide the service or where
          required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>How long I keep it</h2>
        <p>
          I keep enquiry and client correspondence for as long as needed to provide the service and for a reasonable
          period afterward for my own records. If you'd like your information removed, email me and I'll delete it.
        </p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          Under UK data protection law you have the right to access, correct, or delete the personal information I hold
          about you, and to withdraw consent at any time. To exercise any of these, email
          <a href="mailto:promostrats@gmail.com">promostrats@gmail.com</a>. You also have the right to complain to the
          Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at ico.org.uk.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies &amp; analytics</h2>
        <p>
          This site aims to keep tracking to a minimum. If analytics are in use, they are used only to understand
          aggregate traffic and improve the site, never to identify you personally.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>
          I may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a revised "last
          updated" date.
        </p>

        <p class="ps2-legal-note">
          Note: this is a starting template. Review it against how you actually operate — and, if in doubt, have it
          checked by someone qualified — before relying on it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .ps2-legal {
    padding: 72px 0 96px;
  }

  .ps2-legal h1 {
    font-family: var(--ps2-disp);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 4.4vw, 52px);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.04;
    margin-top: 18px;
    color: var(--ps2-ink);
  }

  .ps2-legal-updated {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-family: var(--ps2-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ps2-ink-soft);
  }

  .ps2-legal-body {
    max-width: 68ch;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .ps2-legal-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--ps2-disp);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 22px;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--ps2-ink);
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .ps2-legal-body p {
    margin-top: 14px;
    color: var(--ps2-ink-soft);
    font-size: 16.5px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .ps2-legal-body a {
    color: var(--ps2-cobalt);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ps2-legal-body a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .ps2-legal-note {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--ps2-line);
    font-family: var(--ps2-mono);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--ps2-ink-soft);
    background: #fff;
  }
</style>
